      "value": "<em>You move as swiftly and unpredictably as a flickering flame.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Int 13; Wis 13; Combat Expertise; Perfect Style; base attack bonus +9 or monk level 9th.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>While using Perfect Style, you can use your Wisdom modifier in place of your Charisma modifier when attempting Bluff checks to feint. You can spend 1 ki point as a swift action to gain the benefits of Improved Feint for 1 round.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>You can spend 2 stamina points instead of 1 ki point when using Unblinking Flame Feint.",
